ent-ClothingUniformJumpskirtGothic = готическое платье
    .desc = A gothic dress is an elegant and mysterious garment characterized by its dark and intriguing style. Deep, dark shades like black, burgundy, or navy blue add an aura of mystery and aristocratic allure. Delicate lace accents, luxurious drapery, and ruffles evoke a sense of ancient romance. Keyhole or high neckline cuts give the gothic dress uniqueness and opulence. This dress is perfect for those who want to stand out and emphasize their individuality and mystique. In it, every woman feels refined and captivating, ready to enchant at first sight.
ent-ClothingUniformJumpskirtMaid = платье горничной
    .desc = This refined evening dress, inspired by the elegant maid's style, combines sophistication with a touch of playful femininity. Made from high-quality black satin, it is designed to highlight the refined taste and style of its wearer.
ent-ClothingUniformJumpskirtDressRed = вечернее красное платье
    .desc = This stunning evening gown embodies passion and boldness, blended with elegance and sophistication. Crafted from deep red silk, it captivates attention and exudes luxury and sensuality.
ent-ClothingUniformJumpskirtTango = платье для танго
    .desc = This dress is made for tango, embodying passion and elegance. Its fitted silhouette, with a back cutout and decorative draping, accentuates feminine curves while offering freedom of movement and enhancing the beauty of the dance.
ent-ClothingUniformJumpskirtVictorianBlack = викторианское чёрное платье
    .desc = This black Victorian dress captures the essence of the era. Cutouts, lace, and cuffs add mystery, while the corset creates a refined silhouette. It's perfect for evening events where elegance and intrigue are desired.
ent-ClothingUniformJumpskirtReporter = юбка репортёра
    .desc = A good reporter remains a skeptic for life.
ent-ClothingUniformJumpskirtJournalist = юбка журналиста
    .desc = If journalism is good, it is contradictory by nature.
ent-ClothingUniformJumpskirtVictorianrRed = викторианское красное платье
    .desc = Inspired by Victorian style, this red dress embodies passion and luxury. Intricate details like lace, puffed sleeves, and a voluminous skirt make it the perfect choice for special events where standing out and making an impression is key.
ent-ClothingUniformJumpskirtSuitNurse = форма медсестры
    .desc = This nurse uniform combines functionality and style. Durable, comfortable pants paired with a blouse and signature cap create a professional and neat look, making it an ideal choice for healthcare staff.
ent-ClothingUniformJumpskirtPencilTan = бежевая юбка в стиле «карандаш»
    .desc = The beige "pencil" style skirt exudes softness and elegance. The fitted blazer and straight skirt create a refined silhouette, making it suitable for various occasions, from business meetings to evening dinners.
ent-ClothingUniformJumpskirtPencilCentcomOfficial = юбка «карандаш» официального лица Центкома
    .desc = A strict green "pencil" skirt exudes authority and poise. The fitted blazer and straight skirt form an elegant silhouette, suitable for various occasions, from business meetings to a captain's dismissal.
ent-ClothingUniformJumpskirtPencilSpecialOperationsOfficer = юбка «карандаш» офицера КСО
    .desc = A formal black Special Operations Corps officer's "pencil" skirt embodies authority and sophistication. The tailored blazer and straight skirt create a refined silhouette, suitable for various occasions, from strategic meetings to... well, less conventional operations.
ent-ClothingUniformJumpskirtCargoSalvage = юбка-комбинезон специалиста по утилизации
    .desc = Perfectly pairs with a pickaxe, this versatile and durable skirt jumpsuit is designed for tough work, offering both practicality and a rugged, stylish appearance.
ent-ClothingUniformJumpskirtCargoSalvageFormal = официальная юбка утилизатора
    .desc = Perfectly pairs with a pickaxe, this rugged yet stylish skirt jumpsuit combines functionality and toughness, ideal for salvaging work with a practical, efficient design.
ent-ClothingUniformJumpskirtSalvageLead = юбка-комбинезон ведущего утилизатора
