ent-ClothingUniformJumpskirtCargoFormal = официальная юбка снабжения
    .desc = An official jumpsuit skirt combines practicality with a professional appearance. The tailored design offers comfort and mobility, while maintaining a structured look suitable for work settings requiring efficiency and formality.
ent-ClothingUniformJumpskirtMail = mail technician jumpskirt
