ent-ClothingUniformJumpskirtScientistFormal = официальная юбка учёного
    .desc = A uniform for discerning scientists, best paired with a matching tie, offering a blend of professionalism and intellectual flair. Perfect for prestigious events or high-level research settings.
ent-ClothingUniformJumpskirtCoroner = юбка коронера
